==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Termly
<hw>Term"ly</hw>, <pos>adv.</pos> <def>Term by term; every term.</def>
<mark>[R.]</mark> ⟦ldquo⟧Fees . . . that are <xex>termly</xex>
given.⟦rdquo⟧ <rj><au>Bacon.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
